collectible.author: 0xa7797495e8c8016d0e9cf1d8acdece5b4ac700c4
collectible.description: Angel of Fortune is a Chinese New Year guardian from TingDAO. She wears a traditional tiger head hat, a peach blossom cheongsam full of spring, and her little pink wings spread behind her back. The pink bow and arrow with a Chinese knot is her mysterious magic weapon, which can bring sweetness and good luck to everyone on the occasion of the New Year~
